RACE.RACE_TEXT: LONE STAR PARK RACE 1 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 58. Maiden Special Weight Purse 10000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 119 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RB MARY LYLAH lead the way early while two wide, dueled with DREAM SEQ into the turn, then kicked clear and drew off in the stretch to prevail. DREAM SEQ moved up along the rail to duel for the lead into the turn, then was out kicked and was no match in the end. FLEETS DELITE AA chased the pace while three wide early, moved up to the show position on the turn and held it throughout the stretch. AA BURNING TEMERITY settled while three wide, bid in the late stretch and came up empty. ERIN MHF settled while two wide, bid on the turn and was no threat. RB MAMA WINGATE settled inside and was no threat. UPTOWN KEEPMEINMIND chased the pace while two wide under a strong drive then flattened out. WMA WILD ROSES chased inside briefly then faded and was no rally. WMA DIAMOND GIRL settled back behind the pack and was no factor.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: PEVS KIOTE MOON was bumped at the start, then was in a steady drive behind the leader, was gaining at the top of the lane to edge clear in late stretch and was ridden out to the end to prevail.
